{{> _header title="Avatars" navigation=global.navigation }}
<p>
	Avatars across Fandom should be circular with a 2px internal border.
</p>
<p>
	In order to use Design System Avatars, you need to import <code>/components/_avatar.scss</code>
	partial in your SCSS file.
</p>

<section>
	<h2 id="avatar-square">Square avatar</h2>
	<p>To display an avatar image encapsulated in a square box, use <code class="format-code">.wds-avatar</code> class in your <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> tag.</p>

	{{#component-demo}}
    <img src="images/craig.jpg" alt="user name" class="wds-avatar">
	{{/component-demo}}
</section>

<section>
	<h2 id="avatar-circle">Circle avatar</h2>
	<p>To display a circle avatar, beside <code class="format-code">.wds-avatar</code> class add also <code class="format-code">.wds-is-circle</code> class.</p>

	{{#component-demo}}
    <img src="images/craig.jpg" alt="user name" class="wds-is-circle wds-avatar">
	{{/component-demo}}
</section>
{{> _footer}}
